comments: Bertans (WAS) makes marginal contact to Dinwiddie's (BKN) side on his driving shot attempt.
Jordan (BKN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Napier (WAS) cleanly dislodges the ball from Dinwiddie (BKN) at the end of his drive.
Napier (WAS) engages and separates with Harris (BKN) during the pick.
Napier (WAS) makes hand on ball contact during Dinwiddie's (BKN) upward shooting motion and disengages.
Bryant (WAS) makes contact with Jordan's (BKN) arm and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Hachimura (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dinwiddie (BKN) and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Dinwiddie (BKN) briefly grasps Hachimura's (WAS) arm during the screen and disengages.
Dinwiddie (BKN) is extending his arm into a vertical position as Napier (WAS) gathers the ball and brings his arms into Dinwiddie's on his driving shot attempt.
Bryant (WAS) makes contact to Dinwiddie's (BKN) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Beal (WAS) makes slight contact to Temple's (BKN) body off ball and disengages as he defends the pass.
Jordan (BKN) brings his arm down past a vertical position and makes contact to Bryant's (WAS) arm and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Bryant (WAS) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Dinwiddie (BKN).
Hachimura (WAS) grabs Temple's (BKN) shoulder and front and restricts his ability to reach for the rebound.
LeVert (BKN) commits a take foul on Robinson (WAS).
